import axios from "axios"; import React, { useEffect, useState } from "react"; function Workoutdata(){ const[user,setuser] = useState([]); useEffect(()=> {axios.get('http://localhost:4000/signupdetails') .then(user=>setuser(user.data)).catch(err=>console.log(err)) console.log(user); },[]) return(
{ user.map((data , index)=>

{data.name}

{data.email}

{data.WorkoutDate}

{data.address}

{data.starttime}

{data.endtime}

{data.role}

) }
) } export default Workoutdata
